\section{Abstract}
In this report, we will trying to predict ranks of a sequence of integers(place of the integer in ascending order). Well, it is not very hard to solve the problem but we want to see how the transformer encodes the order through attention and how it beats other methods such as MLP , RNN and LSTM. All the model and its architecture will coded from scratch (however, using pytorch primitives to get a boost in training time).

\section{Baselines}
We will go from MLP to LSTM, and see how they predict the ranks.
